title: Internal Compiler Error - Cannot Relate Bound Region

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
### Code

The breaking code can be found at https://github.com/azulflame/TrainmarchTicketBot/tree/compiler-error
I don't understand the issue well enough to make a MRE by myself.

```> rustc --version --verbose

LLVM version: 15.0.6
```
